Stream application:
Functions included (so far):
person detector
image matching
text extraction

Dependencies:
+libboost-all-dev
+opencv
+pkg-config

Install opencv locally:
-Download latest OpenCV
-in root dir: mkdir build
-cmake . -i
set install dir to /opencv/build in cmake
make && make install

Set path in build.sh and in pkgconfig/opencv.pc

./build.sh
./detect --help
For example:
./detect --walk 1 --image iphone-set/001.jpg --verbose 2
./detect --match matching/queries/206_0001.jpg --database matching/db/
